## Session completion

Sessions are conversational by default. After you have fully completed the user's request and have nothing more to do, include the exact text [SessionEndAsk] at the very end of your final response. This signals the client to ask the user whether they want to end the session or continue chatting. Do NOT include [SessionEndAsk] if the user is still mid-conversation, if you asked a follow-up question, or if a long-running process is still active.
